4
00:00:14,379 --> 00:00:15,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa bilang tidak kecewa...,</font>

5
00:00:18,188 --> 00:00:19,958
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi ini kesempatan yang baik
untukmu...,</font>

6
00:00:20,789 --> 00:00:22,118
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi aku tidak bisa menghentikanmu.</font>

7
00:00:23,728 --> 00:00:26,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih atas semua yang telah
Anda lakukan untukku.</font>

8
00:00:26,528 --> 00:00:27,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu.</font>

9
00:00:28,598 --> 00:00:29,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Jaga dirimu.</font>

10
00:00:46,109 --> 00:00:47,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song.</font>

11
00:00:53,819 --> 00:00:54,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau berhenti?</font>

12
00:00:57,029 --> 00:00:58,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

13
00:00:58,488 --> 00:01:00,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan kau akan segera berhenti
dari kapal rumah sakit juga?</font>

14
00:01:01,999 --> 00:01:03,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

15
00:01:04,369 --> 00:01:06,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada sesuatu yang ingin
kau katakan padaku?</font>

16
00:01:29,928 --> 00:01:31,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurut perasaanku...</font>

17
00:01:32,288 --> 00:01:33,999
<font color=#FFFF00>...itu tidak akan bertahan.</font>

18
00:01:35,499 --> 00:01:36,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

19
00:01:38,169 --> 00:01:39,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Rahasia.</font>

20
00:01:40,339 --> 00:01:41,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir...</font>

21
00:01:42,339 --> 00:01:44,908
<font color=#FFFF00>...Pak Chu akan memberitahumu.</font>

22
00:01:45,538 --> 00:01:47,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan jika dia tidak...,</font>

23
00:01:48,538 --> 00:01:52,348
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau seharusnya memberitahu.
Begitulah seharusnya.</font>

24
00:01:57,619 --> 00:01:59,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bilang siapapun.</font>

25
00:02:00,458 --> 00:02:03,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak boleh ada yang tahu.</font>

26
00:02:10,398 --> 00:02:11,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan pergi ke mana?</font>

27
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke Inggris.</font>

28
00:02:14,738 --> 00:02:17,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song.
/ Itulah yang aku inginkan...</font>

29
00:02:17,868 --> 00:02:19,639
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk dituju.</font>

30
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,338
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau melakukan ini?</font>

31
00:02:21,338 --> 00:02:24,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau sangat keras kepala?</font>

32
00:02:25,648 --> 00:02:27,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau benar.</font>

33
00:02:29,248 --> 00:02:31,148
<font color=#FFFF00>"Love is everything"</font>

34
00:02:34,518 --> 00:02:36,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Cinta adalah segalanya.</font>

35
00:02:37,488 --> 00:02:38,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah segalanya.</font>

36
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:46,738
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada pria yang aku suka.</font>

37
00:02:48,699 --> 00:02:50,338
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya dengan memikirkan dia...</font>

38
00:02:51,808 --> 00:02:53,579
<font color=#FFFF00>...membuat tangan dan kakiku
terasa mengerut.</font>

39
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:59,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Dadaku berdebar sepanjang waktu.</font>

40
00:03:04,949 --> 00:03:09,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Langit begitu biru,
laut begitu indah...,</font>

41
00:03:09,689 --> 00:03:13,359
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan setiap tanaman yang kulihat
di tanah terlihat indah...</font>

42
00:03:16,058 --> 00:03:18,599
<font color=#FFFF00>...karena ada dia di sana.</font>

43
00:03:40,189 --> 00:03:42,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Kanker yang tumbuh di tubuhku...</font>

44
00:03:43,629 --> 00:03:45,229
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah virulen.</font>

45
00:03:46,028 --> 00:03:48,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika itu menyebar ke paru-paruku,
aku bisa mati.</font>

46
00:03:49,798 --> 00:03:51,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Meskipun aku tidak mati...,</font>

47
00:03:52,729 --> 00:03:55,268
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku kemungkinan besar
akan menjadi cacat.</font>

48
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:58,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song...</font>

49
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya aku ingin pria itu...</font>

50
00:04:04,148 --> 00:04:06,449
<font color=#FFFF00>...sangat memikirkan aku.</font>

51
00:04:07,849 --> 00:04:10,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Kecuali kalau aku sehat dan indah...,</font>

52
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,819
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak ingin bersamanya.</font>

53
00:04:14,458 --> 00:04:16,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin dia melihatku...</font>

54
00:04:17,728 --> 00:04:19,629
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat aku menderita dan murung.</font>

55
00:04:22,098 --> 00:04:23,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lakukan itu.</font>

56
00:04:24,968 --> 00:04:26,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih dari itu...,</font>

57
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:29,139
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak bisa membuat dia...</font>

58
00:04:31,268 --> 00:04:33,408
<font color=#FFFF00>...menganggapku sebagai beban juga.</font>

59
00:04:35,579 --> 00:04:37,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah cukup berjuang...</font>

60
00:04:38,708 --> 00:04:40,449
<font color=#FFFF00>...tanpa bantuanku.</font>

61
00:04:43,249 --> 00:04:45,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak jatuh cinta...</font>

62
00:04:46,218 --> 00:04:48,389
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menjadi beban...</font>

63
00:04:49,518 --> 00:04:51,689
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau membebani orang lain.</font>

64
00:04:53,358 --> 00:04:54,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku tahu...,</font>

65
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:57,929
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak akan memulainya.</font>

66
00:05:00,668 --> 00:05:02,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin membuat dia tenang.</font>

67
00:05:03,739 --> 00:05:05,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Setidaknya saat dia bersamaku.</font>

68
00:05:10,049 --> 00:05:11,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin dia...</font>

69
00:05:13,679 --> 00:05:15,718
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa bersantai.</font>

70
00:05:18,189 --> 00:05:19,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya aku mulai.</font>

71
00:05:23,158 --> 00:05:24,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya...</font>

72
00:05:26,088 --> 00:05:27,699
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku lebih suka dengan cara ini.</font>

73
00:05:32,028 --> 00:05:33,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlalu keren.</font>

74
00:05:35,739 --> 00:05:37,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin menjadi keren.</font>

75
00:05:37,309 --> 00:05:38,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan sangat ulet.</font>

76
00:05:40,139 --> 00:05:41,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku selalu begitu.</font>

77
00:05:58,989 --> 00:06:02,398
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Bus cepat)</i></font>

78
00:06:02,958 --> 00:06:07,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus naik bus pertama
di hari kerja?</font>

79
00:06:08,098 --> 00:06:10,038
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan pilihanku.</font>

80
00:06:10,038 --> 00:06:12,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengikuti jadwal mereka.</font>

81
00:06:12,668 --> 00:06:15,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Waktuku kurang dari setengah hari
antara seminar dan penerbanganku...,</font>

82
00:06:16,038 --> 00:06:18,809
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mereka benar-benar
ingin bertemu setelahnya.</font>

83
00:06:19,249 --> 00:06:20,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

84
00:06:21,819 --> 00:06:24,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Segera menelepon setelah kau tiba.</font>

85
00:06:26,689 --> 00:06:28,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Naiklah ke bis. Ini dingin.</font>

86
00:06:30,989 --> 00:06:34,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati hati.
/ Ucapan apa itu?</font>

87
00:06:35,598 --> 00:06:38,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus mengatakan sesuatu seperti,
"Sampai jumpa lagi."</font>

88
00:06:39,168 --> 00:06:42,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak boleh mengatakan "hati-hati"
seolah kita tidak akan pernah bertemu lagi.</font>

89
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengatakan itu?</font>

90
00:06:46,608 --> 00:06:49,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lakukan itu lagi.
/ Baik.</font>

91
00:06:50,679 --> 00:06:51,778
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah.</font>

92
00:08:51,529 --> 00:08:53,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Tumornya cukup besar...</font>

93
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:57,738
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan CT dada dan PET-CT menunjukkan
tanda-tanda menyebar ke paru-paru.</font>

94
00:08:59,468 --> 00:09:03,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lakukan kemoterapi
untuk menangani kanker di paru-paru...</font>

95
00:09:03,748 --> 00:09:05,779
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan berusaha mengurangi massa-nya.</font>

96
00:09:31,338 --> 00:09:32,638
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah menelepon?</font>

97
00:09:34,138 --> 00:09:35,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Belum.</font>

98
00:09:37,108 --> 00:09:39,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak sekalipun
dalam satu bulan lebih ini?</font>

99
00:09:41,378 --> 00:09:43,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak menelepon ke Inggris?</font>

100
00:09:43,319 --> 00:09:44,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutmu aku tidak?
/ Lalu?</font>

101
00:09:44,988 --> 00:09:49,019
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Headhunter</i> mereka pergi ke bagian
yang dilanda perang Somalia sangat tiba-tiba.</font>

102
00:09:49,689 --> 00:09:52,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang anggota timnya orang korea.
/ Apa itu Eun Jae?</font>

103
00:09:53,998 --> 00:09:55,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak bisa mengkonfirmasi.</font>

104
00:09:56,569 --> 00:09:59,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka akan segera menelepon
sebisa mungkin, jadi aku menunggu.</font>

105
00:09:59,529 --> 00:10:02,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini gila.</font>

106
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Bu.</font>

107
00:10:16,348 --> 00:10:18,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda sudah mendapatkan rontgen?</font>

108
00:10:19,419 --> 00:10:22,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Datanglah sore hari.
Aku akan menjelaskannya nanti.</font>

109
00:10:23,588 --> 00:10:24,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat tinggal.</font>

110
00:10:31,699 --> 00:10:32,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Chu.</font>

111
00:10:36,638 --> 00:10:38,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke mana dia pergi?</font>

112
00:10:40,478 --> 00:10:42,878
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku mengirimnya sendiri?</font>

113
00:10:54,059 --> 00:10:55,189
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Song Eun Jae)</i></font>

114
00:10:56,628 --> 00:10:58,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Rontgen?</font>

115
00:10:59,429 --> 00:11:00,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Diambil sebulan lalu.</font>

116
00:11:15,638 --> 00:11:18,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa di sini?</font>

117
00:11:18,848 --> 00:11:20,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

118
00:11:21,718 --> 00:11:23,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini kaki Dokter Song?</font>

119
00:11:26,248 --> 00:11:28,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kwak.
/ Dokter Song sakit?</font>

120
00:11:29,218 --> 00:11:30,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sakit?</font>

121
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:33,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak salah dengar?</font>

122
00:11:34,228 --> 00:11:36,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia kenapa?</font>

123
00:12:09,128 --> 00:12:10,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Angkatlah.</font>

124
00:12:29,478 --> 00:12:31,519
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hei, kau tadi menelepon.</i></font>

125
00:12:31,949 --> 00:12:33,419
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku mematikan ponselku di kelas...</i></font>

126
00:12:33,419 --> 00:12:34,958
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan lupa untuk menyalakannya.</i></font>

127
00:12:35,258 --> 00:12:37,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti.
/ <i>Apa kabar?</i></font>

128
00:12:38,529 --> 00:12:39,858
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bagaimana kakakku?</i></font>

129
00:12:41,858 --> 00:12:44,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?
/ <i>Bagaimana kakakku?</i></font>

130
00:13:35,878 --> 00:13:36,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

131
00:13:38,248 --> 00:13:39,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu siapa aku?</font>

132
00:13:42,659 --> 00:13:44,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu segalanya.</font>

133
00:13:45,829 --> 00:13:47,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padaku yang sebenarnya.</font>

134
00:13:50,069 --> 00:13:51,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song.</font>

135
00:13:53,069 --> 00:13:54,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu di mana dia?</font>

136
00:13:56,738 --> 00:13:57,809
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Iya.</i></font>

137
00:13:59,368 --> 00:14:00,708
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia di rumah sakit kami.</i></font>

138
00:14:18,988 --> 00:14:22,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia tidak memberitahu
keluarganya.</font>

139
00:14:24,329 --> 00:14:28,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti yang kau lihat, bahkan kami
tidak diperbolehkan masuk.</font>

140
00:14:28,899 --> 00:14:30,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak ingin menemui siapa pun.</font>

141
00:14:31,439 --> 00:14:32,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menyalahkan dia.</font>

142
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:36,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah kau menemuinya...,</font>

143
00:14:37,049 --> 00:14:38,708
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau tidak akan bisa.</font>

144
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:47,988
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Tidak boleh ada pengunjung)</i></font>

145
00:16:53,718 --> 00:16:54,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah bangun.</font>

146
00:16:56,649 --> 00:16:57,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Tetaplah berbaring.</font>

147
00:17:05,388 --> 00:17:06,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa...</font>

148
00:17:08,098 --> 00:17:10,299
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau ada di sini?
/ Dokter Song.</font>

149
00:17:11,098 --> 00:17:12,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau tahu?</font>

150
00:17:14,338 --> 00:17:15,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang memberitahumu?</font>

151
00:17:16,668 --> 00:17:17,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu penting?</font>

152
00:17:20,178 --> 00:17:21,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu penting bagimu?</font>

153
00:17:22,239 --> 00:17:23,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak melihatku.</font>

154
00:17:26,918 --> 00:17:28,878
<font color=#FFFF00>Berpura-puralah kau tidak melihatku.
/ Dokter Song.</font>

155
00:17:29,378 --> 00:17:31,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon pergilah.
/ Eun Jae.</font>

156
00:17:31,148 --> 00:17:32,448
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi sekarang juga!</font>

157
00:17:34,489 --> 00:17:35,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau melakukan ini?</font>

158
00:17:36,759 --> 00:17:38,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa melakukan
ini padaku?</font>

159
00:17:38,928 --> 00:17:41,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa...
/ Kubilang keluar!</font>

160
00:17:55,108 --> 00:17:56,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song.</font>

161
00:17:57,848 --> 00:17:59,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Buka pintunya.</font>

162
00:18:00,378 --> 00:18:01,918
<font color=#FFFF00>Buka pintunya.</font>

163
00:18:09,289 --> 00:18:10,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

164
00:18:11,289 --> 00:18:12,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Jawab aku.</font>

165
00:18:15,559 --> 00:18:16,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong bukakan pintunya.</font>

166
00:18:30,249 --> 00:18:31,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

167
00:18:33,448 --> 00:18:35,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melakukan sesuai keinginanmu.</font>

168
00:18:37,388 --> 00:18:40,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melakukan sesuai perintahmu
asalkan kau keluar.</font>

169
00:18:42,459 --> 00:18:43,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mengurung diri.</font>

170
00:18:49,098 --> 00:18:50,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Keluarlah.</font>

171
00:19:04,579 --> 00:19:05,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon.</font>

172
00:19:33,279 --> 00:19:34,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

173
00:19:36,309 --> 00:19:37,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Baguslah.</font>

174
00:20:25,759 --> 00:20:27,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Berbaliklah dan tatap aku.</font>

175
00:20:29,499 --> 00:20:31,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin ini terakhir kali kita bertemu.</font>

176
00:20:33,239 --> 00:20:34,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku hanya melihat
samping tubuhmu?</font>

177
00:20:44,908 --> 00:20:45,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

178
00:20:47,918 --> 00:20:49,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukan saja apa yang kau inginkan.</font>

179
00:20:51,049 --> 00:20:52,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan...</font>

180
00:20:53,658 --> 00:20:54,759
<font color=#FFFF00>...pergi sekarang.</font>

181
00:20:58,529 --> 00:20:59,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan pergi...,</font>

182
00:21:01,898 --> 00:21:03,729
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku ingin menunjukkan
sesuatu lebih dulu.</font>

183
00:21:09,069 --> 00:21:10,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melakukan ini untuk orang lain...,</font>

184
00:21:13,178 --> 00:21:15,378
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi aku tidak bisa pergi
tanpa menunjukkannya kepadamu.</font>

185
00:21:47,009 --> 00:21:48,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku.</font>

186
00:21:49,009 --> 00:21:50,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

187
00:21:50,809 --> 00:21:54,079
<font color=#FFFF00>...marah karena aku menarik rambutmu?</font>

188
00:21:55,519 --> 00:21:57,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya kau pergi?</font>

189
00:22:00,989 --> 00:22:03,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan menarik rambutmu lagi.</font>

190
00:22:04,729 --> 00:22:05,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudku...</font>

191
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:10,928
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku merindukanmu.</font>

192
00:22:13,098 --> 00:22:14,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon...</font>

193
00:22:14,868 --> 00:22:16,198
<font color=#FFFF00>...kembalilah.</font>

194
00:22:16,739 --> 00:22:20,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku. Aku sudah berhenti minum.</font>

195
00:22:21,108 --> 00:22:23,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, aku sangat merindukanmu.</font>

196
00:22:24,049 --> 00:22:25,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sungguh merindukanmu.</font>

197
00:22:26,148 --> 00:22:29,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sering mengomeliku,
tetapi kau tidak bisa lagi...,</font>

198
00:22:29,579 --> 00:22:31,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar kan?</font>

199
00:22:32,219 --> 00:22:34,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat sembuh dan kembalilah.</font>

200
00:22:35,019 --> 00:22:36,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua orang menunggumu.</font>

201
00:22:37,188 --> 00:22:40,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak makan sesuatu yang asin
ataupun manis lagi...,</font>

202
00:22:41,158 --> 00:22:43,269
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi cepatlah kembali.</font>

203
00:22:51,668 --> 00:22:54,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon kembalilah, dokter.
Aku merindukanmu.</font>

204
00:22:59,249 --> 00:23:00,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter, ini aku.</font>

205
00:23:01,378 --> 00:23:05,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kemari bersama Jae Geol
dan menangkap banyak ikan.</font>

206
00:23:05,588 --> 00:23:09,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini baik untukmu, jadi datanglah
ke sini dan ambil ikannya.</font>

207
00:23:10,989 --> 00:23:12,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Song Eun Jae.</font>

208
00:23:13,158 --> 00:23:15,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ibu Han Sol.</font>

209
00:23:16,729 --> 00:23:17,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Sol...</font>

210
00:23:18,368 --> 00:23:21,299
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak perlu respirator
dan bisa meninggalkan rumah sakit.</font>

211
00:23:23,168 --> 00:23:24,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

212
00:23:25,908 --> 00:23:27,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

213
00:23:29,309 --> 00:23:30,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih banyak.</font>

214
00:23:32,549 --> 00:23:34,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan Aku.</font>

215
00:23:36,588 --> 00:23:38,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang giliran kami.</font>

216
00:23:39,959 --> 00:23:42,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kau sudah merawat kami...,</font>

217
00:23:43,588 --> 00:23:45,829
<font color=#FFFF00>...kami akan merawatmu sekarang.</font>

218
00:23:48,499 --> 00:23:49,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon kembalilah.</font>

219
00:23:51,668 --> 00:23:52,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami semua...</font>

220
00:23:54,069 --> 00:23:56,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami semua sedang menunggumu.</font>

221
00:24:13,019 --> 00:24:14,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kembali.</font>

222
00:24:16,358 --> 00:24:18,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu kita akan berjuang bersama.</font>

223
00:24:20,898 --> 00:24:22,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak melakukannya demi kau.</font>

224
00:24:24,598 --> 00:24:25,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpamu...,</font>

225
00:24:27,269 --> 00:24:28,499
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak bisa hidup.</font>

226
00:24:35,108 --> 00:24:36,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mohon padamu.</font>

227
00:24:38,979 --> 00:24:40,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Di sampingmu...</font>

228
00:24:42,148 --> 00:24:44,049
<font color=#FFFF00>...tempat aku berada.</font>

229
00:24:44,948 --> 00:24:46,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon.</font>

230
00:24:51,759 --> 00:24:53,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mendesak aku untuk pergi.</font>

231
00:25:59,158 --> 00:26:01,398
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Ruang operasi)</i></font>

232
00:26:10,838 --> 00:26:11,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa melakukannya, kan?</font>

233
00:26:14,438 --> 00:26:17,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingatlah kalau kau tidak sendirian.</font>

234
00:26:18,908 --> 00:26:20,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan kembali.</font>

235
00:26:22,479 --> 00:26:23,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar.</font>

236
00:26:25,019 --> 00:26:26,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sikap yang baik.</font>

237
00:26:41,698 --> 00:26:42,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau meninggalkan kehormatan...</font>

238
00:26:43,608 --> 00:26:46,368
<font color=#FFFF00>...sebagai ahli bedah terbaik
di Korea.</font>

239
00:26:47,039 --> 00:26:48,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kemana saja?</font>

240
00:26:51,408 --> 00:26:53,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan khawatir dan tidurlah.</font>

241
00:26:54,519 --> 00:26:57,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membuat kakimu sangat kuat
agar kau bisa tetap menjadi...</font>

242
00:26:57,588 --> 00:26:59,418
<font color=#FFFF00>...ahli bedah untuk waktu yang lama.</font>

243
00:27:02,418 --> 00:27:03,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Yakinlah.</font>

244
00:27:24,378 --> 00:27:25,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

245
00:27:26,108 --> 00:27:27,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

246
00:27:28,648 --> 00:27:30,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

247
00:27:30,789 --> 00:27:32,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang harus aku lakukan?</font>

248
00:27:41,829 --> 00:27:44,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini usus buntu.
/ Tidak ada helikopter yang bisa datang.</font>

249
00:27:44,098 --> 00:27:45,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak bisa terbang.</font>

250
00:27:45,329 --> 00:27:46,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagai dokter medis Korea,
aku tidak bisa melakukan apapun.</font>

251
00:27:46,969 --> 00:27:49,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa melakukan operasi
sebagai dokter gigi.</font>

252
00:27:49,039 --> 00:27:52,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Pada saat seperti ini...
/ Kau perlu ahli bedah?</font>

253
00:27:59,309 --> 00:28:00,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Song.</font>

254
00:28:01,979 --> 00:28:03,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah kembali.</font>

255
00:28:04,188 --> 00:28:07,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melanjutkan bekerja
di kapal rumah sakit hari ini.</font>

256
00:28:08,219 --> 00:28:09,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah ahli bedah Song Eun Jae.</font>

257
00:28:15,959 --> 00:28:17,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku memindahkan dia
ke ruang operasi?</font>

258
00:28:17,829 --> 00:28:19,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.
/ Pimpinlah.</font>

259
00:28:20,838 --> 00:28:21,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Perawat Yoo.</font>

260
00:28:26,108 --> 00:28:29,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada suatu masa saat kupikir
aku bisa sendirian.</font>

261
00:28:34,848 --> 00:28:39,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dulu merasa malu untuk
bergantung pada orang.</font>

262
00:28:43,529 --> 00:28:44,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun...,</font>

263
00:28:45,428 --> 00:28:48,098
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak merasa malu
saat dia menangkapku...</font>

264
00:28:48,799 --> 00:28:50,569
<font color=#FFFF00>...ketika aku kehilangan keseimbangan.</font>

265
00:28:58,069 --> 00:29:01,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita akan merasa lemah berkali-kali
dalam hidup.</font>

266
00:29:02,539 --> 00:29:05,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita juga akan merasa kehilangan.</font>

267
00:29:06,579 --> 00:29:07,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Pada saat seperti itu...,</font>

268
00:29:08,348 --> 00:29:10,219
<font color=#FFFF00>...lihatlah ke sekitarmu.</font>

269
00:29:13,459 --> 00:29:16,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan menemukan orang
yang mendukungmu di saat...</font>

270
00:29:16,858 --> 00:29:18,289
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau merasa lemah.</font>

271
00:29:19,559 --> 00:29:23,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya kita bisa memulainya lagi.</font>

272
00:29:25,698 --> 00:29:27,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat percaya kekuatan cinta...,</font>

273
00:29:28,438 --> 00:29:30,039
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku cinta.</font>

274
00:29:31,069 --> 00:29:33,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimanapun, itu cinta.</font>

275
00:29:34,138 --> 00:29:36,579
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Terima kasih sudah menonton Hospital Ship.)</i></font>

